{"tid":2431931,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紐約州長科莫就性騷擾指控道歉：「我從沒不當地觸摸別人，我當時不知道我令人感到不舒服。」但強調不會辭職","createTime":"2021-03-04T03:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T04:09:57.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"76bc4836971c66cf2cb9ba736dc82ce044197367","tid":2431931,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:42:38.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】被指涉及性騷擾的紐約州州長科莫，就自己可能令人感到不舒服的行為道歉，但強調不會辭職。<br />\n<br />\n美國紐約州州長科莫：「我從沒不當地觸摸別人，我當時不知道我令人感到不舒服。若我真的令人感到不舒服，而我現在知道真的有這樣做，我為此道歉。我不會辭職，我為紐約州民眾工作，他們選擇了我，我將會服務紐約州民眾。」<br />\n<br />\n科莫在記者會又指，會配合州檢察部門就他涉及性騷擾所作的調查，科莫兩名前女助手日前指控科莫涉及性騷擾，包括強吻和作出不當言論。近日再有一名女子指，科莫曾撫摸她的背部，又問可否親吻她。連串事件引起民眾不滿，要求科莫辭職。"},{"pid":"a898e437e4e7ead766d735c760637214f32a06ef","tid":2431931,"uid":235754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:49:31.000Z","msg":"同777一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f906f5c4e1a0b322e47cda1a6f623ebd650be6e","tid":2431931,"uid":144431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:53:45.000Z","msg":"左膠真係無敵，平時成日cancel人，但自己就immune to cancel culture"},{"pid":"2e50b1e7da18cef99f44f60c0f31365583002134","tid":2431931,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:55:46.000Z","msg":"沒不當接觸人都係跟大佬學姐<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/8422640384/hFCD48F41/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.chzbgr.com%2Ffull%2F8422640384%2FhFCD48F41%2F&h=32386ebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PsLrOYn.gif?noredirect\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPsLrOYn.gif%3Fnoredirect&h=4b69ea8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pxv4RJT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpxv4RJT.gif&h=42011766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dyjC3Po.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum